   <Description _locID="App_Description"><!-- _locComment_text="{MaxLength=10000} App Description" -->
Play open source video formats found on the web today. This includes video files that are stored in the OGG video container and videos that use the Vorbis or Theora codecs. After you install Web Media Extensions, you can play these kinds of videos in Microsoft Edge or in a video app installed on Windows 10.

Included technologies:
• OGG Container Parser
• Vorbis Decoder
• Theora Decoder
   </Description>

